FROM: One Earth Electronics
TO: Recent customers
SUBJECT: Service follow-up
SENT: August 30, 4:30 P.M.
Dear customer,
Thank you for contacting our online support service for help with your electronic device. Please take a moment to tell us about your experience. Your feedback and suggestions are valuable to us.
Directions: Respond to the e-mail. In your e-mail, make TWO suggestions and ask ONE question.

Item3.content: Do you think it is better for an individual to have a role model who is a celebrity, or a role model who the individual knows personally? Why? Give reasons and examples to support your opinion.
